item.title: CVE-2020-11073|2024-08-04T11:21:14.525Z -- michaelaquilina -- zsh-autoswitch-virtualenv
item.description: In Autoswitch Python Virtualenv before version 0.16.0, a user who enters a directory with a malicious `.venv` file could run arbitrary code without any user interaction. This is fixed in version: 1.16.0
